    "However, the generative capabilities of decoderonly models allow us to cast NLU tasks in a novel light by extracting the output from the generated text.",
    "In this study, we are using instruction fine-tuning, zero-shot, and few-shot learning as approaches to perform intent classification and sentiment analysis.Instruction fine-tuning [23] leverages the generative power of LLMs by training them on explicit instructions alongside the usual data.",
    "In the context of intent classification or sentiment analysis, instructions can be like \"detect the intent of the sentence\" or \"identify the sentiment of this utterance\".",
